Detailed Description

RTCORBA::SharedMemoryProtocolProperties implementation.

Stores Shared Memory Protocol configuration properties.

Member Function Documentation

CORBA::Boolean TAO_SMEM_Properties::_tao_decode (  TAO_InputCDR &    in_cdr )  [virtual]
 

This method reads an instance of SMEMProperties from a CDR encapsulation. This Protocol Property in TAO specific, so there is no order of encapsulation specified in the RT CORBA Spec. The current implementation expect the field according to the order of declaration.

Reimplemented from RTCORBA::ProtocolProperties.

CORBA::Boolean TAO_SMEM_Properties::_tao_encode (  TAO_OutputCDR &    out_cdr )  [virtual]
 

This method writes the CDR encapsulation of an instance of SMEMProperties. This Protocol Property in TAO specific, so there is no order of encapsulation specified in the RT CORBA Spec. The current implementation encodes the field according to the order of declaration.

Reimplemented from RTCORBA::ProtocolProperties.
